name: Spinetto Keyboard POV
description: This is a self portrait at the cybercafe from the Spinetto Shopping Center computer PC Keyboard point of view. A short-handed man and his wife watch me over the counter. In a moment, I get startled by a red light in front of me. The door opens. The man behind his desk picks up the box from under the counter. I shake it. He makes it through the door. "Hello." He says. I look at the profile picture of himself in the mail, he stare at me for a third time."It's yours. It's mine." I say. "Why, ma'am?
